# MongoDB Java Quickstart

Various quick starts for using mongodb with java & scala - check the different branches for different versions of the driver

To run:  `./gradlew run`
or to supply a different connection string: `./gradlew run -DconnectionString=mongodb://localhost`

Source code is in `./src/main/scala/quickstart/QuickStart.scala`
Github source: https://github.com/rozza/mongo-java-quickstart
